  "title": "Quality Control Executive (Food Science) | Training Provided | Boon Lay - YZ11",
  "description": "<p>Quality Control Executive</p><p>Working days: 5-day work week <br />Working hours: 9am to 6pm<br />Work location: 3 Buroh Lane (Boon Lay)<br />Salary: $2300 - $2800</p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Ensure the food manufacturing process comply with food safety standards, specifications, and government and industry regulations.</li><li>Assist in the implementation and maintenance of ISO 22000, FSSC 22000, Halal and SFA documentation and standards.</li><li>Conduct routine inspections of production processes to ensure compliance with regulatory standards and perform routine in-process checks on products.</li><li>Support regulatory inspection, customer audits and visits and to follow-up with corrective action and documents, when necessary.</li><li>Responsible for reporting any non-conformance of products / process and timely reporting to the Executive / Manager.</li><li>Other ad-hoc duties as required.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Knows how to use MS Office.</li><li>Able to work in chilly environment (10°C to 15°C).</li><li>Preferably a Diploma in Food Science, Food Technology or equivalent.</li><li>Preferably knowledgeable in local & international food safety standards</li></ul><p><br /></p><p>Tan Yen Zhen (Chen Yan Zhen) Reg No: R25138932</p><p>The SupremeHR Advisory Pte Ltd EA No: 14C7279</p>",
